         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">MELBOURNE BOTANICAL GARDENS. ¶ To the Editor of the Argus. ¶ Sir, — ¶  ¶ As probably a numerous attendance at the bazaar to be held to-morrow again in the Botanical Gardens will reward the great exert...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">57.11.27</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To the Editor of the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Argus</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found. The text given here is from 'Melbourne Botanical Gardens',<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Argus</seg>,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>28 November<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>1857, <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>p. 5 (B57.11.01.</p>
               </note>MELBOURNE BOTANICAL GARDENS.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: center; font-style: italic; "
               xml:lang="en">To the Editor of the Argus.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir, —</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>As probably a numerous attendance at the bazaar to be held to-morrow again in the Botanical Gardens will reward the great exertions of so many benevolent ladies for a noble purpose,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In the expectation that the bazaar would attract a large crowd, Henry Kay, the Clerk of the Executive Council, wrote to the Police Chief, Charles MaMahon, to ask somewhat<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>diffidently<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>whether some police constables could be assigned to the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Botanic Garden to help maintain order, and the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>request was granted (Unit 1, VPRS 1199 Chief Commissioner's inward correspondence, VA 724 Victoria Police, Public Record<seg rend="apple-converted-space" style=""> </seg>Office, Victoria).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I hope you will kindly permit me to draw, through your esteemed paper, the attention of those visitors who value our acquisition of very rare plants to a beautiful specimen of the New Zealand palm lily (<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Cordyline Australis</seg>), now for the first time flowering in this establishment. It is very conspicuous in the north eastern portion of the garden, near the lagoon.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mr. Johnson, the band-master, kindly informs us that we shall enjoy the following music to-morrow:—</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">March — Leichhardt's — Marsh.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Overture — Fidelio — Beethoven.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Cavatina — Sonnambula — Bellini.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Waltz — Werber zum Tanz — Labitzki.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Selection — Stabat Mater — Rossini.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Quadrille — Como — D'Albert.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Harmonious Blacksmith (by desire) — Handel.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Polka — Young Couple — Coote.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Selection — Irish Melodies (by desire) — Johnson.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Galop — Austrian.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Most obediently yours,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>FREDK<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Typesetters error for<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>Ferd<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">?</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>. MUELLER.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">27th November, 1857.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plantnames"
               style="font-style: italic; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Cordyline Australis</p>
         </div>
